        <div1 type="summary">
            <p><add hand="#barker">Receipt for slave Richmond. Inclosure gives expense account of the Negro.</add></p>
        </div1>
        <div1 type="body">
            

<p>Received from <persName>Moses Austin</persName> a <persName>Negro man</persName> by the name of 
<persName>Richmond </persName>the property of <persName>Stephen Fuller Austin esqr</persName> who is now so 
diseased that he is not able to travel and who is placed under the care
of <persName>Doct Rivers</persName> and in case of his Removal to be placed under some
Other if Necessary, to be restored to health, now be it remembered,
that so soon as said <persName>Negro man</persName> is in a situation to labour I agree to
pay Twelve Dollars pr month for the hire of said <persName>Negro </persName>and which
money so accruing&#8212;from the labour of said <persName>Negro </persName>is to be retained
in my hands to discharge <persName>Doct Rivers</persName> bill and any other <persName>Doct</persName>s Bill if
any other is employed and also his board untill he commences labour,
Unless the said expences are other wise discharged either by the said
<persName>Stephen Fuller Austin</persName> or the said <persName>Austin </persName>or there order in which
case I promis to deliver said <persName>Negro man Richmond</persName> to the said
<persName>Austin </persName>or his <persName>son </persName>or there order Death and other Circumstances not<pb n="376"/>
with in the Control of the Undersignd (Excepted) Twelve Dollars is
to be allow.d pr month for the board of said <persName>Negro </persName>untill able to
labour, but if I can hire out the said <persName>Negro man</persName> for more than
Twelve Dollars pr month I am to do so and account to the said
<persName>Austin </persName>for the same.</p>

<p><persName>Douglass Foksythe </persName>   [Rubric]</p>
<p><hi rend="italic"><date when="1821-01-22">Jany 22th 1821</date></hi></p>
<p><persName>Joshua Parker</persName> [Witness?]</p>

<p>Sr <persName>Mr Hugh McGuffen</persName> has full authority to call for the within Named
<persName>Negro man Richmond </persName>and Receive him on discharging his bills of
expense</p>
<p><persName>Moses Austin </persName>   [Rubric]</p>

<p><date when="1821-02-10">Feby 10 <hi rend="italic">1821</hi></date></p>
<p>To <hi rend="italic"><persName>Dugless Forsythe Esq</persName></hi></p>

<p>Recd the within named <persName>negro </persName>from <persName>D. Forsythe</persName> <date when="1821-07-15">July 15, 1821</date></p>

<p><persName>S. F. Austin.</persName></p>
<p>[Inclosure]</p>
<p><persName>Stephen F. Austin</persName></p>

<p>To <persName>D Forsythe</persName> Dr</p>

<p><date n="01-xx-1821">Jany 1821</date>	To <persName>Moses Austin</persName>s bill_________________________________	8. 50

<date when="1821-02-20">Feby 20</date>     " 1 pr. pantaloons for your <persName>negro Richmond</persName>____________     	3. 00
		1 Shirt for do________________________________________     	2. 50

<date when="1821-04-28">April 28</date>    1 pr pantaloons_______________________________________     	2. 50
		1 "  Leather do_______________________________________     	3. 00
		1  shirt______________________________________________     	2. 50
