											    $70. 75</p>

<p>Recd a draft on <persName>A Sampyrac</persName> for the above Seventy Dollars 75/100
which when paid will be in full.</p>
<p><date when="1821-07-16">July 16th 1821</date>                                                     <persName>Douglass Forsythe</persName></p>

